You should receive a response that includes data from DeepSeek and the analysis from your AI model.AI Assistance uses AI models to provide automated, real-time responses or insights based on user input. It helps users by answering queries, offering suggestions, or assisting with tasks, enhancing efficiency in applications like customer support or virtual assistants.AI Data Analysis enables AI models to process and extract insights from large datasets. It identifies patterns and trends, aiding data-driven decision-making. This is crucial for applications where analyzing data quickly and accurately leads to better business outcomes.Integrating  with  offers a robust solution for building AI-powered applications that can
